description:
Influencer culture is Stephanie McNeal’s bread and butter, and today the BuzzFeed editor joins us to talk about the influencer reckoning of 2020, who she thinks came out winners (and who fumbled the ball spectacularly) and of course, her favorite bike shorts. Which are now MY favorite bike shorts, because I bought them too and I have been wearing them all week.
